q{ Q:"Minimum energy to launch satellite of mass m from planet mass M radius R into circular orbit at altitude 2R" A:"d" O:a)"2GmM/(3R)",b)"GmM/(2R)",c)"GmM/(3R)",d)"5GmM/(6R)" R:"Total energy in orbit at radius 3R: E = -GMm/(2*(3R)) = -GMm/(6R). Initial at surface: E_i = -GMm/R. Energy required = E_f - E_i = -GMm/(6R) + GMm/R = (5/6) GMm/R." }

q{ Q:"Vehicle mass M moving with momentum P on rough road, coefficient μ_k. Distance travelled before rest is" A:"a" O:a)"P²/(2μ_k M² g)",b)"2μ_k M² g / P²",c)"P²/(2μ_k g)",d)"P² M²/(2μ_k g)" R:"Kinetic energy = P²/(2M). Work done by friction = μ_k M g d. Equate: d = P²/(2μ_k M² g)." }

q{ Q:"Projectile initial velocity i+2j (i horizontal, j vertical, g=10). Equation of trajectory" A:"a" O:a)"y = 2x - 5x²",b)"4y = 2x - 5x²",c)"4y = 2x - 25x²",d)"y = x - 5x²" R:"u_x=1, u_y=2. x = t, y = 2t - (1/2)gt² = 2x - 5x²." }

