q{ Q:"Air column closed at one end length 32cm in resonance with tuning fork. Open tube length 66cm in resonance with another fork. They produce 8 beats/s. Frequencies are (fundamental)" A:"c" O:a)"250Hz,258Hz",b)"240Hz,248Hz",c)"264Hz,256Hz",d)"280Hz,272Hz" R:"Closed: f1 = v/(4L1) = v/(4*0.32)= v/1.28. Open: f2 = v/(2L2)= v/(2*0.66)= v/1.32. Ratio f1/f2 = (1.32)/(1.28)=1.03125. Difference f1-f2 =8. Solve v/1.28 - v/1.32 =8 → v(1/1.28-1/1.32)=8 → v(0.78125-0.7575758)=8 → v(0.0236742)=8 → v≈338 m/s. Then f1=338/1.28=264Hz, f2=338/1.32=256Hz." }

